{"tid":858582,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"生三個仲咁fit！50歲李婉華 晒噴血三點式巨乳照","createTime":"2018-10-12T01:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T09:14:20.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bf781c0b4d98cf3403eef99aedf718e63f781b6f","tid":858582,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/81/Yfrog.png/revision/latest?cb=20060509155958\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F81%2FYfrog.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060509155958&h=9f6c92a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年50歲嘅李婉華近年移居加拿大，近日佢同家人去墨西哥度假，李婉華喺facebook貼咗幾張三點式泳照，身材依然火辣，點睇都唔似係三子女之母，而且李婉華外貌跟廿年前相差不遠！<br />\n<br />\n90年代花旦之一嘅李婉華係，當年拍過不少劇集及電影，仲同吳鎮宇、何家勁拍過拖，但兩段情都未能開花結果，最終婉華嫁畀圈外男，仲生咗一女及一對孖仔，好幸福！"},{"pid":"1739023884a707d3d1dc04cd091b7f5477873fc6","tid":858582,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89230b5dda08885d726226964596bbaa24eb1a09","tid":858582,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T02:00:07.000Z","msg":"50歲李婉華 生三個仲咁fit<br />\n<br />\n現年50歲的李婉華已移居加拿大多年，雖然佢已是三子女的媽咪，但身材仍然保養得宜，近日李婉華同家人去咗墨西哥旅行，佢事後喺facebook上載泳照，穿上紅色三點式的她身材依然好fit，絕對係辣媽一名！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/81/Yfrog.png/revision/latest?cb=20060509155958\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F81%2FYfrog.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060509155958&h=9f6c92a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/81/Yfrog.png/revision/latest?cb=20060509155958\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F81%2FYfrog.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060509155958&h=9f6c92a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/81/Yfrog.png/revision/latest?cb=20060509155958\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F81%2FYfrog.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060509155958&h=9f6c92a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/81/Yfrog.png/revision/latest?cb=20060509155958\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F81%2FYfrog.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060509155958&h=9f6c92a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/81/Yfrog.png/revision/latest?cb=20060509155958\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F81%2FYfrog.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060509155958&h=9f6c92a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/81/Yfrog.png/revision/latest?cb=20060509155958\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F81%2FYfrog.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060509155958&h=9f6c92a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d55f991c40ebf0dacefb2c9d9c1eb0968ad5da7","tid":858582,"uid":28743,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"好耐無見過黃蛙"},{"pid":"e261f6f875d0a9a6401aad573ddd70f5d0de3693","tid":858582,"uid":12190,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T02:00:37.000Z","msg":"屌 好耐冇見過青蛙圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /